ZH: 能不能请你帮我一个忙？
EN: Can you please help me with something?

ZH: 能不能告诉我怎么去火车站？
EN: Can you tell me how to get to the train station?

ZH: 能不能给我一杯水？
EN: Can you give me a glass of water?

ZH: 能不能考虑一下我的建议？
EN: Can you consider my suggestion?

ZH: 能不能等一会儿？
EN: Can you wait for a moment?

ZH: 能不能跟我说慢一点？
EN: Can you speak slower with me?

ZH: 你能不能别再吃零食了？
EN: Can you stop eating snacks?

ZH: 能不能请你开灯？
EN: Can you please turn on the light?

ZH: 能不能告诉我你的手机号码？
EN: Can you tell me your phone number?

ZH: 能不能给我一些建议？
EN: Can you give me some advice?

ZH: 能不能跟我一起散步？
EN: Can you take a walk with me?

ZH: 能不能借我一本书？
EN: Can you lend me a book?

ZH: 能不能不要说这个话题？
EN: Can you not talk about this topic?

ZH: 能不能陪我去医院？
EN: Can you accompany me to the hospital?

ZH: 能不能带我去买东西？
EN: Can you take me shopping?

ZH: 能不能告诉我你的名字？
EN: Can you tell me your name?

ZH: 能不能给我一点钱？
EN: Can you give me some money?

ZH: 能不能请你不要吵？
EN: Can you please be quiet?

ZH: 能不能跟我练习一下汉语？
EN: Can you practice Chinese with me?

ZH: 能不能等我一会儿？
EN: Can you wait for me for a while?
